    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been pampered since day one and is in such incredible shape that it practically looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Seriously, it\u2019s a total stunner and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019d love for you to come by and see it for yourself\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
      "price": 46500.0,
