    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of the S54-powered legend. Featuring the high-revving 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, the powertrain delivers linear thrust and a signature metallic rasp. The ZF 6-speed manual transmission offers tactile, short-throw engagement, paired with a variable M-differential lock for superior power delivery. Mechanically flawless, this chassis has undergone documented preventative subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service. The suspension geometry remains factory-taut with zero bushing deflection, and the original paint retains its deep, showroom luster. A concours-ready specimen for the discerning purist.",
